0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b13dbb4e0f5e16cda46aebb9163e05688953dd","tid":886051,"uid":24662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"巴打10日好似真係有啲多 <br />\n不過如果有一日半日多左冇咩野做<br />\n都可以分享下有咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭metro 紅色M2線到 <strong><em>Blaha Lujza t&eacute;r</em></strong> 呢個站<br />\n如果英文自問可以嘅可以去 <strong><em>Erkel Theater </em></strong>睇下musical / drama (因為佢都係匈牙利話+英文字幕，仲要出得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n個陣有半日時間無無聊聊就去左個到睇左套 billy elliot  （最主要係因為國家劇院個邊裝修緊同過左open hour) <br />\n記得價錢都好抵睇好似80幾hkd per one 不過可能我學生所以一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N3UiFyU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN3UiFyU.png&h=4591e53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果睇完musical又fit到時間<br />\n又想食鵝肝個類傳統啲嘅匈牙利菜<br />\n可以去<strong><em>Lado cafe </em></strong>到試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知其他地方有啲更出名<br />\n但呢間就價錢味道環境都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個人叫左2個餐湯，2杯飲品，兩個courses<br />\n都只係400hkd左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鵝肝係好抵食好似200hkd左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMPCbDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMPCbDG.png&h=8f0dcb05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8xoRDH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8xoRDH.png&h=c5a5ca64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Lwdusf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Lwdusf.png&h=a7b660c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外間野大概夜晚8點開始有band show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然最好就bk好位先<br />\n<br />\n近住 St. Stephen&lsquo;s Basilica 間雪糕店 <strong><em>Gelarto Rosa</em></strong>幾好味又可以呃下like <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢隻hazelnut chocolate 真心推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75Wduui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75Wduui.png&h=31702961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係如果真係去浴場<br />\n除左毛巾沖涼液個啲外<br />\n緊記要攞對拖鞋<br />\n唔係你一定後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣我去塞切尼溫泉浴場<br />\n又咁好彩播緊world cup <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWQedXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWQedXn.png&h=9b115429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjWXWaJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjWXWaJ.png&h=a892cf31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似寫得太長似遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望幫到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7937667d624f759bb66b718c3943708c2aae29","tid":886051,"uid":55810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後就係如果真係去浴場<br />\n除左毛巾沖涼液個啲外<br />\n緊記要攞對拖鞋<br />\n唔係你一定後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣我去塞切尼溫泉浴場<br />\n又咁好彩播緊world cup <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWQedXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWQedXn.png&h=9b115429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjWXWaJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjWXWaJ.png&h=a892cf31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似寫得太長似遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望幫到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n浴場我冇入到去 好似好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過影相好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368113ab6c1c4fd4827f955fe4ff39838feadaa0","tid":886051,"uid":24662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7937667d624f759bb66b718c3943708c2aae29","tid":886051,"uid":55810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後就係如果真係去浴場<br />\n除左毛巾沖涼液個啲外<br />\n緊記要攞對拖鞋<br />\n唔係你一定後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣我去塞切尼溫泉浴場<br />\n又咁好彩播緊world cup <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWQedXn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWQedXn.png&h=9b115429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjWXWaJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjWXWaJ.png&h=a892cf31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似寫得太長似遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望幫到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n浴場我冇入到去 好似好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過影相好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:25:21.000Z","msg":"個地下係幾污糟下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都算值得入去睇下<br />\n可以當去個靚靚嘅游泳池咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647de182b6aa16dec3b9cb867176653b48818555","tid":886051,"uid":81540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"提提你M3 line under reconstruction 淨係weekday 先開, National theatre 都係裝修緊冇表演睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e54b44c5493d4adb4c21f1fac12bb96c282d443","tid":886051,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:38:51.000Z","msg":"個個講牛肉湯喺邊度飲架?<br />\n定求其一間餐廳都有?"},{"pid":"e3b40a286ace5a38b5ece64d87be88ea07ea12d3","tid":886051,"uid":55810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647de182b6aa16dec3b9cb867176653b48818555","tid":886051,"uid":81540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"提提你M3 line under reconstruction 淨係weekday 先開, National theatre 都係裝修緊冇表演睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T18:31:52.000Z","msg":"同埋M3係最早收 夜晚落到去冇車on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過地面有巴士一樣叫M3補位<br />\n<br />\n你都可以download個app叫BKK嚟睇交通"},{"pid":"7b39f5df57d7d220664ad1b47608322d2904172c","tid":886051,"uid":79786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"布達佩斯十日?<br />\n我3日都悶到西咁"},{"pid":"283323ad309e8085935076e248d80390c4438a30","tid":886051,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:24:51.000Z","msg":"去埋附近啦緊係10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533457f39ccac6055e26beb7fd5aedda9c611b97","tid":886051,"uid":205105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:36:27.000Z","msg":"去the hospital in the rock<br />\n<br />\n講佢地俾俄佬打同埋冷戰時期佢地有咩措施對核戰"},{"pid":"5da12de78e8dc76478de447ea57f876f7f4775e8","tid":886051,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b39f5df57d7d220664ad1b47608322d2904172c","tid":886051,"uid":79786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"布達佩斯十日?<br />\n我3日都悶到西咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"認同，去完覺得比連登仔老點左<br />\n除左食嘢平，消費平，唔覺有咩特別<br />\n<br />\nmusical 嘢不如去Vienna ，上網有教點買平飛，雖則平時消費貴過Budapest，但可以兼顧埋shopping (鋪頭冇咁齊，退稅d店員話係退番匈牙利錢）<br />\n<br />\n講景色附近布拉格，ck，hallstatt，Salzburg，國王湖，天鵝堡好好多<br />\n上述地方比你嘅感覺係古色古香，Budapest 係陳舊嘅感覺<br />\n呢樣係睇相唔覺，但去到會感覺到<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔太建議搭regiojet 過Budapest, 之後要轉metro, 但個站好多露宿者，企定係個售票機問人攞錢嘅人，同埋好多眼神閃縮嘅人，不過係platform 同市區又冇乜嘢<br />\n一係落到站直接沖去metro 個info用credit card 買完飛就走<br />\n<br />\nstay 1-2日係Budapest睇大路嘢同買手信就夠，留d 時間去多幾個東歐地方啦"},{"pid":"1014b2947cf928151ddf126aed7b67bd1481ea68","tid":886051,"uid":118616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T20:31:59.000Z","msg":"年尾年頭會去10日奧捷匈 有無人一齊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}